<p>There has been a lot of discussion of how command line parameters should be parsed.  At the moment there are no plans of adding more functionality to what Raku provides out of the box.</p>

<p>If you want more tweakability, you should probably look at the <a href="https://modules.raku.org/dist/Getopt::Long:cpan:LEONT" rel="noreferrer">Getopt::Long module</a> by <em>Leon Timmermans</em></p>
